      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VICTORY EXAM (3) comes off an average run last start when fifth at this track over 525m behind Magic Bocca (30.75) in a Mix 6/7. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can discover winning form. SOMEBODY TOLD ME (2) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with his maiden win, then finished a 11 length fourth last start at this track over 525m (30.50). Nicely drawn here. Well placed here and should do much better. KIWI EDDIE (4) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth at this track, but was among the placings at Horsham three back. Can turn it around this time. REAL WORLD (7) can feature with the right run.",
